      "text": [
        "2582 - وَ رَوَى جَابِرٌ عَنْ أَبِي جَعْفَرٍ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ أَنَّهُ قَالَ : «لاَ بَأْسَ أَنْ يُلَبِّيَ اَلْجُنُبُ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2582 - Jabir narrated from Abu Ja'far (as) that he said:\n\"There is no harm in a junub (someone in a state of major ritual impurity) reciting the Talbiyah.\""
        ]
      }
    }
